    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1947-07-11T16:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-07-11T16:00:00-05:00" n="476"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d476">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">880.00/6–2047: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Embassy in France</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1947-07-11T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 11, 1947—5 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2556. We have carefully studied and are in full accord with both findings and
                    recommendations contained <gloss target="#t_urtel1">urtel</gloss> 2442<note
                        n="1" xml:id="d476fn1">See footnote 2, <ref target="#pg_691">p.
                        691</ref>.</note> and <gloss target="#t_urdesp1">urdesp</gloss> 9033 June
                    20.</p>
                <p>We believe present time is propitious and therefore you should make recommended
                    oral approach at highest level. If you have any strong reasons for not acting
                    immediately please inform Dept.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
